snippet.title: SNES Longplay [250] Do-Re-Mi Fantasy - Milon no Dokidoki Daibouken (Fan-Translation)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: SCHLAUCHI

Superb sequel to the terrible Milon´s Secret Castle!
Compared to the terrible prequel Milons Secret Castle, this sequel is awesome!
Great gameplay, great graphics, great music! Unfortunately this was only released in Japan! For this longplay im using the fan-translated version!

There is one minigame that i didnt enter as it would hang in the emu! -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
